Media
Manga
Written and illustrated by Makoto Kudo, My Awkward Senpai initially began as a webcomic published on Kudo's Twitter account published on March 2, 2019. It later began serialization in Square Enix's  manga magazine Young Gangan on December 6, 2019. Its chapters have been collected into ten  volumes as of September 2025. The series is published in English by Comikey and by Square Enix through their Manga UP! Global app.
