Anime
An anime television series adaptation was announced on December 16, 2024. It is produced by Studio Elle and directed by Ayumu Kotake, with series composition by Mio Inoue, character designs by Kenrō Tokuda and music composition by Kōji Fujimoto. The series premiered on October 2, 2025, on Tokyo MX and other networks. The opening theme song is , performed by Angela, while the ending theme song is , performed by Ami Maeshima. Crunchyroll is streaming the series.
